Events.title: DI Awareness Worshop on India AI Impact Summit 2026 and Digital India Initiatives in Sikkim
Events.summary: A workshop on Digital India awareness was held in Sikkim, focusing on the India AI Impact Summit 2026 and Digital India initiatives. The event aimed to raise awareness about the impact of AI and digital initiatives in the region. The workshop was part of the Digital India program, promoting digital literacy and AI adoption in Sikkim.
